snippet.title: День рождения Дианы, 5 лет! Diana's 5th Birthday Party
snippet.description:
День рождения Дианы, 5 лет!
1.04.2019 Diana is 5 years old! We had a really fun birthday party for her, full of her friends, surprises and gifts! Thank you so much for your love and support! Happy Birthday Diana!
Diana's INSTAGRAM https://www.instagram.com/kidsdianashow/
